issue.title: phpunit.xsd is not valid
issue.body:
In line 20 whitelist is duplicated in choice and causes this validation error in eclipse:

```
cos-nonambig: whitelist and whitelist (or elements from their substitution group) violate "Unique Particle Attribution". During validation against this schema, ambiguity would be created for those two particles.
```

body:
I am not particularly good at XSDs either, but `xmllint` has no problem:

```
$ xmllint --schema phpunit.xsd --noout phpunit.xml
phpunit.xml validates
```
Looks like @kubawerlos is not responding and that it is up to you, @theseer.
@kubawerlos Can you please send a pull request that only contains your changes to `phpunit.xsd`? Thanks!
I do not see a pull request for this.
Nevermind, I was looking in the wrong place.
